data.description: Beautiful home located in Perris! This home features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a loft and is 2327 square feet. The home was updated with new kitchen cabinets, new counter tops, new carpet, new paint, new window coverings and new tile flooring within the past 18 months. This home shows pride of ownership in every way. Inside the home features a formal dining room and a formal living room. The family room is open to the extra large kitchen area. The kitchen features white appliances, white tile counter tops and has plenty of room for a table and chairs with plenty of counter and cabinet space! All bedrooms are located upstairs, along with a large open loft area that could be used an office/playroom or second family room. The spacious backyard is completely landscaped and you have no neighbors behind you. Home is currently under contract for a home security system- equipment stays, but the lease transfers with the sellers. This home shows like a model home, you won't be disappointed! No HOA! Located close to the freeway, parks, schools, restaurants, and shopping. Home sweet home awaits you!  Call Heather at (951)265-1329 for info!
data.whatILove: Pride of ownership.. this home shows like a model home!  You won't be disappointed.
